will say, now, remember, this is just my opinion and observation. Please do not take this as direction.

00:07:34.560 --> 00:07:39.680
The members of the publishing committee may have a different perspective. Isn't that beautiful?

00:07:39.680 --> 00:07:46.240
Even the governing body members understand that their authority has boundaries. What a good

00:07:46.240 --> 00:07:52.959
example for us to follow. As we know in the secular world, the more responsibility one has,

00:07:53.680 --> 00:07:59.360
the more authority they have. But isn't it true that it's exactly the opposite within Jehovah's

