00:08:31.040 --> 00:08:38.799
we uphold Jehovah's authority and his right to rule his way. Now, we contrast all of that with

00:08:38.799 --> 00:08:45.679
Satan, who promotes independence and doing his own things, sets up rival and competing organization

00:08:45.679 --> 00:08:52.720
arrangements and has no idea of the limits of his authority. So really, it drives home the point in

